<HEADLINE> UAE President Meets with Bush </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ABU DHABI, March 18 (Xinhua) -- President Sheikh Zayed bin
Sultan al Nahyan of the United Arab Emirates (UAE) today met with
visiting former U.S. President George Bush.
</P>
<P>
