The visit already took him to Saudi Arabia, where he met with
King Fahd and was decorated with this kingdom's highest honor, the
King Abdul-Aziz Medallion, and Oman, where he met with Sultan
Qaboos.
</P>
<P>
The former U.S. president is reported to be planning to visit
Kuwait, Qatar, Lebanon and Syria. 
