<HEADLINE> Burundi President To Visit Kenya </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NAIROBI, March 18 (Xinhua) -- President Sylvestre
Ntibantunganya of Burundi will arrive in Nairobi on Tuesday to
attend a Burundi ambassadors conference.
</P>
