<HEADLINE> hke031855 - World Bowls Championship Open in Adelaide </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CANBERRA, March 18 (Xinhua) -- The Eighth World Bowls
Championships opened here today, with host Australia winning both
first round matches in pairs and triples events.
</P>
<P>
