foreign delegations. They were Wen Jiabao, head of the Communist
Party of China delegation; Do Muoi, Secretary-General of the
Vietnam Workers' Party; Norodom Ranariddh, Chairman of the
Funcinpec Party of Cambodia; and Chea Sim, Chairman of the
Cambodian People's Party.
</P>
<P>
Following a 15-minute opening ceremony presided over by
President Nouhak Phoumsavan, Party President Khamtay delivered a
38-page-long political report.
</P>
<P>
In his report, Khamtay summarized the achievements and
shortcomings of the renovation process and the implemenation of
the resolution of the Fifth Congress of the party held five years
ago, and also set up targets, policies and guidelines for the next
five years until 2000. 
