<HEADLINE> Legend Top on List of Best PC Producers: Survey </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, March 18 (Xinhua) China's own computer giant, the
Legend Computer Group, has roared to top place in the highly
competitive home PC market.
</P>
<P>
The Beijing based company's market share in personal computers
ranked first, and the prestige of its products was also on top of
the list, the national newspaper People's Daily reported today.
</P>
<P>
According to a national survey of consumers launched by the
All-China Journalists Association, and the People's Daily, the
company took the lion's share of PC family market, with their PC
products the best known, and liked by domestic consumers.
</P>
<P>
The company was the first company in China to lower the price
of personal computers with Pentium processors to less than 10,000
yuan (1,204 US dollars), the paper said.
</P>
<P>
It quoted Yang Yuanqing, assistant president of the company,
said Legend sold 100,000 PCs last year, with total tax and profits
reaching 70 million yuan. 
</P>
